{
  "texts": [
    "The dynamic nature of transformers, combined with the foundational knowledge captured in word vectors, has made them the state-of-the-art choice for many NLP applications.",
    "What makes transformer model better for NLP tasksIn this section, we introduced several special mechanisms in the transformer model.",
    "Self-attention [1]There are many similarities between self-attention and attention, but the transformer model uses self-attention to understand and translate other related words into a translation method of the word we are dealing with.",
    "Let us look at an example: a wolf does not want to eat a rabbit because it is too thin.",
    "Does it represent a wolf or a rabbit?"
  ]
}